Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:13.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:26.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:31.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:38.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:57.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:07.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:14.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:20.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:27.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:13.15,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.07,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.20,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光晕  浮现于黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:26.42,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,未见未知的阳光  会将谁照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:31.17,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的伙伴  就算沉浸于悲伤也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.14,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:38.43,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  来伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.81,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿过这片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.02,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  冲击全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:46.65,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.32,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,紧盯着世界的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:57.16,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,当小小胸膛填满了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:07.08,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,琥珀之梦  朝着约定的地点出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:14.47,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,对你的关心关爱  比这天空更宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:20.60,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,无限扩张  永无止境
Comment: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:27.52,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.40,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:27.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}住み慣れたこの街を出てゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}新しい世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:35.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}まだ見ぬ色を　探しに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I can not do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:42.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}素直になれないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}あの虹の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}行ってみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:56.10,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}頭に浮かんだイメージを抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:02.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I will never ever give up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:10.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}どこまでも　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wanna make my life shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:28.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}輝くよ　あの虹の向こうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.86,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:27.99,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}离开这熟悉的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:31.16,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}去探索新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:35.08,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}寻找从未见过的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.54,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:42.51,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}有时也会不够坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.64,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那彩虹的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.47,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想试着去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:56.10,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}记住浮现在头脑中的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:02.94,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我永远不会半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:10.54,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}不论到哪里  不论走多远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:17.54,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想让自己的生命更闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:28.47,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}释放光芒吧  直到那彩虹的彼端
